# ZEAZ Platform — Complete ZMaster Execution Prompt

Target repository: `cvsz/zeaz-platform`  
Target local root: `/home/zeazdev/zeaz-platform`  
Purpose: AI-agent readable execution prompt for completing ZEAZ Platform refactor work safely, including audit, PostgreSQL readiness, secure local env generation, Docker hygiene, port normalization, Cloudflare Tunnel routing through Nginx, app startup checks, app consolidation reports, and final verification.

