# Completion Checklist

```text
A ZMaster run is complete only when:
1. All required reports exist or blockers are documented.
2. All required scripts exist and are executable.
3. Cloudflare Tunnel config routes public hostnames through Nginx.
4. Nginx maps public domains to canonical app ports.
5. Validators derive host/port expectations from the canonical map.
6. The verifier uses safe temporary files and writes structured JSON.
7. No real secret is committed.
8. No Docker volume is pruned by default.
9. The final integration report includes exact next commands.
```
